      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Comparison with alternatives"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "TypedDict gives static hints only — no runtime validation. jsonschema library validates dict against JSON Schema without Python models. Marshmallow similar to Pydantic v1 patterns. Pydantic v2 is standard for FastAPI and modern agent frameworks."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Security and reliability"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Validation prevents injection of unexpected fields that might alter tool behavior. Cap string lengths and array sizes to avoid DoS via huge model outputs. Never eval() parsed JSON — use json.loads + Pydantic only."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Mental model"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Parsing JSON tells you the envelope is well formed; validation checks the "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "customs form",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "bold"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " matches what the tool expects before letting goods into the warehouse."
          }
        ]
      },
